      "content": "thanks for those! chapel hill and lake norman sound like exactly what we're looking for. honestly though, we're a bit worried about moving into areas that might be too... i don't know, unpredictable? like we really want to avoid any areas with high crime rates or districts that struggle with stability and social issues. are there any specific neighborhoods or districts in those states you'd suggest we avoid just to be safe? maybe places that are a bit more diverse or have higher turnover? just want to make sure we're making the right choice for the kids.",
